---
import GitHubIcon from "./icons/GitHubIcon.astro"
---

<section id="proyectos" class="mt-20">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
        Proyectos Destacados
    </h2>

    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="flex flex-col bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-xl p-6 hover:bg-slate-700/80 hover:border-blue-500/50 transition-all group">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">AutoParts</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4 flex-1 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                Plataforma web de e-commerce para la venta de repuestos automotrices y visualización de información, detalle 
                y carrito de compras con su respectivo backend. <br>
                Proyecto Academico desarrolado con:
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
                <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/python/python-original.svg" alt="Python" title="Python" class="w-8 h-8 hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" />
                <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/django/django-plain.svg" alt="Django" title="Django" class="w-8 h-8 hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 bg-white/90 rounded-sm p-1" />
                <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/javascript/javascript-original.svg" alt="JavaScript" title="JavaScript" class="w-8 h-8 hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 rounded-sm" />
                <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/css3/css3-original.svg" alt="CSS3" title="CSS3" class="w-8 h-8 hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" />
            </div>
            <a href="https://github.com/yovngmamba8/autoparts" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 font-medium transition-colors mt-auto">
                <GitHubIcon class="w-5 h-5" />
                Ver Proyecto en GitHub
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-xl p-6 hover:bg-slate-700/80 hover:border-blue-500/50 transition-all group">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">QA: AutoParts</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4 flex-1 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                Diseño y ejecución del plan integral de pruebas para el sistema AutoParts, asegurando la robustez y 
                calidad del software. <br>
                Proyecto Academico de automatización de pruebas desarrollado con:
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
                <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/python/python-original.svg" alt="Python" title="Python Scripts" class="w-8 h-8 hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" />
                <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/selenium/selenium-original.svg" alt="Selenium WebDriver" title="Selenium WebDriver" class="w-8 h-8 hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" />
                <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/pytest/pytest-plain.svg" alt="Pytest" title="Pytest" class="w-8 h-8 hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" />
            </div>
            
            <a href="https://github.com/yovngmamba8/plan-pruebas-autoparts" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 font-medium transition-colors mt-auto">
                <GitHubIcon class="w-5 h-5" />
                Ver Documentación
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-xl p-6 hover:bg-slate-700/80 hover:border-blue-500/50 transition-all group">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Portfolio Web</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4 flex-1 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                Portfolio Web realizado para dar a conocer mis habilidades adquiridas en mi educación superior
                y proyectos los cuales realicé a lo largo de mi formación. <br>
                Proyecto Personal de desarrollo de este portfolio web desarrollado con:
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
                <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/astro/astro-original.svg" alt="Astro" title="Astro" class="w-8 h-8 hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 bg-white/90 rounded-sm p-1" />
                <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/tailwindcss/tailwindcss-original.svg" alt="Tailwind CSS" title="Tailwind CSS" class="w-8 h-8 hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" />
                <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/javascript/javascript-original.svg" alt="JavaScript" title="JavaScript" class="w-8 h-8 hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 rounded-sm" />
            </div>
            
            <a href="https://github.com/yovngmamba8/plan-pruebas-autoparts" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 font-medium transition-colors mt-auto">
                <GitHubIcon class="w-5 h-5" />
                Ver codigo en GitHub
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

